Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay. Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shoot me like you did back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "the end"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen "the end of the world," time and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "the end"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die, and I'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the actual, horrible story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:37.03,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(288,200)\pos(363,340)}I'm Home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This actual, horrible story...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The various things I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The various stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I told to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was taken from the room at the Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and placed in a pitch black room with no walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I touched felt funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A room without an up or down, left or right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I knew someone was observing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A completely silent room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Sometimes, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,faintly heard screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meals were provided from some unknown place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I counted the number of meals I was given...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven, twelve, thirteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-one, twenty-three...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I could no longer keep track\Nof the number of meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that man was standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.60,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:06:00.73,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,A little child like you shouldn't be wandering\Naround in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.32,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is the child who...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:08.74,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.75,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're cute..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.00,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.76,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful. How beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.39,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here. This is the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.76,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.26,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Our achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.77,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.27,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.77,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.16,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only remember bits and pieces of the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.49,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,by the achievement of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.58,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,new... this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.79,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,know... we, selected comrades... propose a toast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.92,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,to the future of our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:00.92,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.50,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first person collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several people ran towards him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who ran towards him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also started collapsing, falling down, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Groans...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yells...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear filled the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forty-two people who were there died...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for one man, Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to escape from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice when my arm was scratched\Nby the thorns in the rose garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived at the Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you welcomed me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,telling you all that I had experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the one who said "welcome home"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who said that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.27,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.52,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only listened to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was taken to the Rose Mansion was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was taken to the Rose Mansion was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was taken and dragged\Ndown the stairs in the Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was counting the meals in the\Npitch black room, the one without walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was standing in the\Nmidst of all those dead people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.76,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.05,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.70,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.20,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.21,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for days and days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Johan what I experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan thought my experience was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan thought my experience was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that Johan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Johan everything just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan listened to my story...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he looked like he was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he also looked like he was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such an expression before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he will probably destroy himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I'm destroying myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where would I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A car was found near a lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell off a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edward was killed in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who did this was probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going to kill Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His son lives in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Johan about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that will put an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that will calm his madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sister's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that are missing from her memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was there one more memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... what we were trying to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place you should go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place we should go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely get there someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's great to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a rare visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just making tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to try my famous tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a special herb tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have something important to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me what it is you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you going to kill next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the strange jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did I raise so much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did I kill all those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the final scene so many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I see a different scene now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true final scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memory that only I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where I should truly go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where I should go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruhenheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.95,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.34,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:25.88,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:34.30,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.76,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
